Plugins that integrate with the cascade palette can each ship a single help tiddler — typically at `$:/plugins/<author>/<plugin>/help` — tagged `$:/tags/rimir/cascade-palette/help` with `ca-group: Plugin: <slug>`. Drill into this row to browse them.

